WEBVTT

1
00:00:01.000 --> 00:00:04.000
Big Buck Bunny

2
00:00:05.000 --> 00:00:08.000
A Blender Foundation Production

3
00:00:10.000 --> 00:00:14.000
In a beautiful meadow, a large bunny
wakes up from his peaceful slumber.

4
00:00:15.000 --> 00:00:19.000
He stretches and yawns,
enjoying the warmth of the sun.

5
00:00:20.000 --> 00:00:24.000
The bunny notices a butterfly
flying gracefully nearby.

6
00:00:25.000 --> 00:00:29.000
He watches it with curiosity
and gentle amusement.

7
00:00:30.000 --> 00:00:34.000
Suddenly, three mischievous rodents
appear in the forest.

8
00:00:35.000 --> 00:00:39.000
They spot the peaceful bunny
and plan their pranks.

9
00:00:40.000 --> 00:00:44.000
The rodents begin their mean-spirited
tricks on the unsuspecting bunny.

10
00:00:45.000 --> 00:00:49.000
They throw nuts and acorns
at the gentle giant.

11
00:00:50.000 --> 00:00:54.000
The bunny tries to ignore them,
but they persist with their antics.

12
00:00:55.000 --> 00:00:59.000
Finally, the bunny has had enough
of their bullying behavior.

13
00:01:00.000 --> 00:01:04.000
He decides to teach the rodents
a lesson they won't forget.

14
00:01:05.000 --> 00:01:09.000
The bunny starts planning
his clever revenge.

15
00:01:10.000 --> 00:01:14.000
He sets up an elaborate trap
using natural materials.

16
00:01:15.000 --> 00:01:19.000
The rodents, unaware of the trap,
continue their mischief.

17
00:01:20.000 --> 00:01:24.000
One by one, they fall victim
to the bunny's clever schemes.

18
00:01:25.000 --> 00:01:29.000
The first rodent gets launched
high into the sky.

19
00:01:30.000 --> 00:01:34.000
The second rodent meets
a similar fate.

20
00:01:35.000 --> 00:01:39.000
The third rodent tries to escape
but it's too late.

21
00:01:40.000 --> 00:01:44.000
All three rodents learn
a valuable lesson.

22
00:01:45.000 --> 00:01:49.000
The bunny returns to his peaceful meadow,
satisfied with justice served.

23
00:01:50.000 --> 00:01:54.000
Peace returns to the forest
once again.

24
00:01:55.000 --> 00:01:59.000
The butterfly returns to visit
the gentle bunny.

25
00:02:00.000 --> 00:02:04.000
Together they enjoy the beauty
of the natural world.

26
00:02:05.000 --> 00:02:09.000
The bunny smiles contentedly,
grateful for the peaceful moment.

27
00:02:10.000 --> 00:02:14.000
Nature's harmony is restored
in the meadow.

28
00:02:15.000 --> 00:02:19.000
And the bunny lives happily
ever after.

29
00:02:20.000 --> 00:02:24.000
The End

